    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Usagi Sekai - Bunny Shaman is a short Deck Builder, atmospheric experience. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against corrupted spirits, cleanse the corrupt tendrils infecting your village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras/f160ed6ef5009d421b4a9b1189295fe8.avif?t=1765885631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras_big/f160ed6ef5009d421b4a9b1189295fe8.avif?t=1765885631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies with your deck of attack, defense, and special ability cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras/6cc072c2020e31e6c0794acb5d94102c.avif?t=1765885631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras_big/6cc072c2020e31e6c0794acb5d94102c.avif?t=1765885631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden powerful cards and strategize your fight against the heart of the corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras/724f45279029359bb493710d96bf655c.avif?t=1765885631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras_big/724f45279029359bb493710d96bf655c.avif?t=1765885631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work your way through combat as effectively as possible. Banishing low level enemies might not be worth the ultimate cost...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras/888177b24624d6720912b18d54972f30.avif?t=1765885631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299380/extras_big/888177b24624d6720912b18d54972f30.avif?t=1765885631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
